## History ## {#history}

* Version 0.1: 19 October 2021 (initial draft, [link](https://github.com/OwnYourData/soya/blob/main/docs/https://github.com/OwnYourData/soya/blob/main/docs/SOyA_WhitePaper_Nov21.pdf))
