Structures {#structure_element}
----------

All artefacts ([=terms/bases=] and [=terms/overlays=]) in SOyA are declared in a [=terms/structure=] and it holds the following information:
* meta    
    * name    
    * context    
    * namespace    
* content    
    * bases    
    * overlays    

